==English==
===Etymology===
from [[silver]] and [[dollar]]
===Noun===
{{en-noun}}
# {{US}} A [[dollar]] [[coin]], whether made from [[silver]] or not. 
#:'' In Las Vegas, many of the slot machines use '''silver dollars'''. ''
# {{US}} A small [[pancake]].
#:'' Alice went to the diner and ordered a stack of '''silver dollars''' with butter and blueberry syrup. ''
# Several species of tropical freshwater fish of the genus ''Metynnis'', of the family [[Characidae]], of which ''[[w:Metynnis argenteus|M. argenteus]]'' is one; popular for [[aquarium]]s; so named from their shape and flashing silver color.

